  "description": "This charming 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom apartment is perfectly located in the heart of Estepona Old Town, one of the most beautiful and authentic areas on the Costa del Sol. Nestled on a quiet street yet just moments from the buzz, it offers the ideal balance of tranquility and convenience.\n\nThe apartment is only a 5-minute walk to the beach and within easy walking distance of everything Estepona has to offer — restaurants, cafés, bars, shops, and seaside promenades. A car is absolutely not needed, making it perfect for a relaxed, stress-free stay.\n\nInside, the apartment features a bright open-plan kitchen and living area, creating a comfortable and welcoming space. The bathroom has been recently renovated and includes a modern walk-in shower. The bedroom is cozy and inviting, ideal for unwinding after a day at the beach or exploring town.\n\nFull of character and charm, this is a beautiful little apartment in a truly unbeatable location — perfect for couples, solo travelers, or anyone wanting to experience the real Estepona lifestyle.\n\nPlease note that we welcome families and couples only, no groups under 30, and no hen or stag parties. Should you fall outside of this category but wish to book nonetheless, please send us an enquiry detailing a bit more about yourself and the group that you will be travelling with so we can request this for you.",
